article.description: — Malik Curry had 24 points as Old Dominion defeated William & Mary 86-78 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Curry leads Old Dominion over William & Mary 86-78
article.linkText: Curry leads Old Dominion over William & Mary 86-78
article.story: NORFOLK, Va. -- — Malik Curry had 24 points as Old Dominion defeated William & Mary 86-78 on Saturday night. A.J. Oliver II had 19 points for Old Dominion (1-1). Joe Reece added 13 points. Jaylin Hunter had 11 points. Connor Kochera had 19 points for the Tribe (0-1). Luke Loewe added 16 points and 10 assists. Yuri Covington had 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ Elements of this story were generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
